ICBCIBMContest.controller

类 QrRCodeGenerateController

  • java.lang.Object
    • ICBCIBMContest.controller.QrRCodeGenerateController

  • @Controller
 @RequestMapping(value="/qr")
public class QrRCodeGenerateController
extends java.lang.Object
    该类为二维码生成控制器层核心类，接收前端传来的数据并返回封装了响应的 API 传输对象 依赖于 QrGeneratorService PropertiesFactory APITransitObjectFactory 
     
      success:
      {
          data: "http://qr.topscan.com/api.php?text=示例值详见响应示例",
          msg: "转换成功",
          status: "0"
      },
      fail:
      {
          data: "null",
          msg: "参数不完整",
          status: "400011"
      }
    作者:
    Mr.Hu
